The Sovereign Charter: Mandate of the Global Hemp Nation
31 December 2025
“The Sovereign Charter: Mandate of the Global Hemp Nation”


Preamble: By the authority vested in the Global Hemp Ledger and through the demonstrated commitment to the Equity Index 2.0, this Charter delineates the rights, responsibilities, and privileges of “The Sovereign” within the Planet Hemp Global Cooperative. This status is earned through the cumulative contribution of 5,000 Experience Points (XP), signifying unparalleled dedication to the principles of Nature, Data, and Future.

